115
00:05:01,509 --> 00:05:04,220
of Mel Gibson's directorial
follow-up to <i>Braveheart</i>,

116
00:05:04,304 --> 00:05:06,306
a remake of the Jimmy Stewart classic,

117
00:05:06,389 --> 00:05:07,974
<i>Mr. Smith Goes To Washington.</i>

118
00:05:08,057 --> 00:05:09,350
(applause and cheers)

119
00:05:09,434 --> 00:05:11,477
