132
00:05:31,748 --> 00:05:33,291
Ah, for cryin' out, Glayvin!

133
00:05:34,334 --> 00:05:35,585
Is Mel Gibson here?

134
00:05:35,668 --> 00:05:37,628
No, sorry, but like all celebrities,

135
00:05:37,712 --> 00:05:40,673
