benefits for various diseases.

136
00:05:40,757 --> 00:05:43,593
(applause and cheers)

137
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:49,182
-(gasping)
-Did they like it?

138
00:05:49,265 --> 00:05:50,808
Well, they haven't seen it yet, Mel.

139
00:05:50,892 --> 00:05:52,643
How'd you get here from LA so fast?

140
00:05:52,727 --> 00:05:54,270
