156
00:06:19,087 --> 00:06:20,546
What, even better than the original?

157
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,923
'Cause that was pretty fabulous, too.

158
00:06:23,966 --> 00:06:25,551
<i>...And he fought for them once.</i>

159
