who ran the savings and loan.

167
00:06:43,694 --> 00:06:44,529
Shh!

168
00:06:44,946 --> 00:06:46,114
(all murmuring)

169
00:06:46,197 --> 00:06:47,115
Excellent.

170
00:06:47,865 --> 00:06:49,700
